review_content: This stunning peachy pink shade truly works for everyone! I usually prefer more rose or mauve based shades (Antonym's Rose Blush is a personal favorite), so I wasn't sure how this shade would work for me, but it truly looks incredible on. It brings a flush of luminosity to your skin that instantly will perk up any complexion - a must have!

user_specs: ['Eye Color Brown', 'Hair color Blonde', 'Skin Tone Medium', 'Skin Type Combination']
review_content: Super natural easy to use, I am not an expert but simply love this blush it gives you a lift from within, healthy looking glow something we all look to have from our makeup

Love this as a highlighter/luminizer, and that's how I use it most of the time. If I'm in a rush, it works as a pretty blush but the shimmer is a bit much for a blush for me. I have medium-olive undertone skin and it works for me. The staying power isn't great unless you set it, and looks like just shimmer and no color after a sweaty work out. I'm willing to deal since it's an organic brand.
